casebody.data:
Leslie REDMOND, petitioner,
v.
Jody R. UPTON, Warden. No. 13-7159. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 2, 2013. Case below, --- Fed.Appx. ----, 2013 WL 5915761 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
